Dialogs.Dialog: You were talking to someone right now, weren't you?
It's been a while since we talked properly like this.
You are the only one who speaks to me.
Yes, it looks like fun. Then I'll go back.
Ah... Emm, wouldn't be misunderstood if your girlfriend-san saw you?
Ah... I'll go out with you again.
You're always doing your best. Is life fulfilling after all?
Excuse me. If I have any trouble, can I ask for your help?... I think I better not.
I think beign with your girlfriend-san is important, but club activities as well.
To go out with someone of the opposite sex... I wonder how it feels.
Sometimes you can hear your girlfriend-san's stories. It's wonderful.
Is it that good with girlfriend-san? I'm kidding, sorry.
I want to have fun... It's okay to think so once in a while.
Do you want to go out with girlfriend-san on your days off?
Lately, making sweets has been a lot of fun.
Is it difficult to live alone? Awesome...
It's amazing that the library committe's working. Have you forced yourcelf into club activities?
Part-time job seems to be difficult. School, club activities... it's great.
If you don't do it seriously, you could get injured. Take care.
I see. Don't overdo it, do your best okay?
Oh,▲高嶺＊＊▲. I'm still a long way off.
No, that's not true. It's amazing.
I'm doing... fine, I guess. Just a little sloppy.
Fufu, just sloppy. Give your best.
▲主人公＊▲. Do you want me to help you?
I see. If something happens, please talk to me.
Excuse me. Recently, how is it going between us? Is it going well?
Yes... I'm looking at you, and I wonder...
...No, it's nothing. Fufu, I think it's better to get along.
I know. Excuse me, I got something like this...
Hmm? Oh, it's ▲特別デートアイテム＊＊▲.
I have no use for it... If you'd like, you can have it.
Eh, it's okay? Then, I'm happy...
Yes, it is. I would like you to use it with your girlfriend.
Um, maybe I'm caring to much, but...
I wonder if it's better not to talk to someone who has a girlfriend.
I would feel bad for her...
I knew it... I'm sorry, I'll be careful.
Is that so? If so, I'm glad.
You're a friend. It's all good.
It's been a while since we talked like this.
You know, if you talk to me like before, it would be useless.
You know. You may have changed a little recently.
I think it's your atmosphere... I think that.
I wonder what it sounds like, a cool impression, I guess.
Possitive feeling... Yeah, I think so.
Oh, come to think of it, girlfriend-san has changed her hairstyle.
I noticed that kind of thing.
I'm a little worried. I wonder if I do it for you.
Recently, I heard you're getting better.
Who says it... Is that right?
That's what many people said. So, I'm sure that's the case.
Excuse me... I think it's a way of helping to say this...
Recently, I heard that your girlfriend-san is feeling sick... what happened?
I won't ask anymore... just think about it.
The other day, when you were together with girlfriend-san, I saw you again.
Lovers do that kind of thing, after all...
I'm sorry. I saw your guys on a date last week.
Haha... did you now. You don't have to apologize.
But it seems like I'm peeping on you, so I wonder if I'm wrong.
Hmm, we're just dating, we're not doing anything bad.
（Come to think of it, I've been on dates a lot lately）
Hey, aren't you going out with girlfriend-san?
I'm not sure, but... I guess you want to do it.
I'm sorry, I said something unnecessary.
At school... that kind of thing...
I don't think it's a violation of school rules or something like that...
▲主人公＊▲. You've been working really hard lately.
Because you have a good reputation at school. You're in great shape! That's it.
That's great, but don't overdo it.
（Come to think of it, I wonder about it...）
You are still on a relationship with girlfriend-san.
I've been thinking that lately... I wonder if it's not going well.
Relationship?... Ah, my girlfriend. I think it's going well.
That's not the case... well, that's how it is.
That's right... Well, there are time when we get along better.
It seems you're doing well with girlfriend-san recently.
Huh, how do you know that?
Somehow... when I look at you.
I see... I'm getting a little shy.
Because everyone says that. I wonder if that is the case.
Hmm, I wonder if we were looked at like that... Well, it's good.
...Sorry you seem a bit different. Something happened?
Somehow... when I look at your face...
Well... I got on a fight with my girlfriend...
Speaking of which, I wonder if I've emailed her recently...
...I guess not. I'm not very good at it, but sending e-mails is important.
That's right... I guess that's true.
Maybe... maybe you'd be happy if I emailed you.
Mmmm... I wonder if you've been getting enough love these days.
（I wonder if I should kiss her）
Ah... The other day, I left my date alone...
I'm not the one you should apologize to. I think it's better you make up for it.
The other day... I left my girlfriend alone during the date, she got angry and went home.
For that... I would be angry too.
You have to apologize so that I can forgive you.
Lately, maybe I don't see my girlfriend that much.
I see... then, she might feel lonely.
I think it's better to contact girlfriend-san...
Somehow, I was feeling bad and I was curious... I hope you didn't overdo it.
（Is it my fault? I was careful...）
Is your girlfriend-san resting from a cold?
I'm worried. I would be happy if you could visit her.
A visit... That's true, thank you.
You know... it was a while ago, but... we went out together.
You didn't have a girlfriend at that time.
Yes, I remember it once in a while. And even now, we're getting along like this. Thank you.
You know, I remember... that was the same as before...
I told you that... I loved you.
Now that you have a girlfriend, we're still friends...
Are you going home now? If you don't mind, can I tag along?
It's okay, I don't have any plans. Let's go back home.
I'm going home with my girlfriend...
Oh, right. Don't worry. See you.
I'm sorry, I'm going home alone today.
I guess I kept you waiting. Are you alright?
Yes, I'm okay. I was talking to my friend a while ago.
That so. Then, shall we go?
Well then, we arrived. Bye bye.
... No, I'm sorry. It's nothing, bye bye.
I wonder if that's not bad.
▲高嶺＊＊▲ is good at making sweets, it's a show of her skills.
But, that's it. Isn't that a little lonely?
It's not hard, but... Well, I think it's better to have fun.
Isn't it fun for▲高嶺＊＊▲? You can have something back, right?
That's right... Yes, I guess it's fun.
You know. Well, today is my birthday.
Thank you. Fufu, I made you say it.
It's okay, let me say it!
Geez. What are you trying to do.
Thank you for remembering. Don't tell me, are you planning something?
That... would be bad for girlfriend-san.
I see, good thing you noticed. Thank you.
Hmm. That's why I'm afraid of just saying that much.
It's Christmas... are you going to spend it with girlfriend-san?
Actually, I had something to ask you...
I want to hear the opinion of a girl. I'm sorry, in advance.
I don't know if it will be useful... Yes, I'll do my best.
It looks fun to look into various things. A study of a woman's mind!... I'm kidding.
Hello. It's▲苗字▲, but I have a request.
A gift for my girlfriend... it would be nice.
Thank you, I want to hear an opinion from a girl.
That would be me? I have to give a serious reply.
Haha, you don't have to be so serious. Thank you.
▲主人公＊▲. I'm sorry I've kept you waiting.
I wasn't waiting. Thank you, it was a sudden request.
No, it's okay. Besides, it's a peculiar gift, and you don't want girlfriend- san to be sad, do you?
Haha, you're so reliable. Let's work together.
▲高嶺＊＊▲. Did you find something good?
Yeah... I saw something over there...
（▲高嶺＊＊▲ is serious even at times like this...）
Oh, sorry. I went on my own... what happened?
Did she misunderstood something? What should I do?
▲高嶺＊＊▲ Don't worry about it. It's okay. So, how was it?
You saved me today. Thank you, really.
Don't mention it, I hope it was helpful.
Well, you know, it was sudden.
So, are you two going out?
Well, I guess that's the way it is.
...That so, give your best. I'm going now.
（▲高嶺＊＊▲, I wonder if she saw...）
Your relationship with girlfriend-san. It seems like you are doing it for a long time...
Yes. Especially avoid light- hearted behavior at school.
Your relationship with girlfriend-san may have gone too far.
...Maybe that's right, but from my point of view, it's gone too far.
Why can you do that now... without hesitating so much?
Eh, what about... are you talking about my girlfriend?
That's right. It's good to be on good terms, but remember you are a high school student, okay?
I'm a high school student... I'm going to do it, should I make a report it?
I knew it, I wonder if girlfriend-san is having a hard time.
You say that, but you're a little lazy...
I'm sure you're having a lot of troubles...
I think it's going great with your girlfriend-san.
I don't think I'm such a selfish person...
Yes, I'm on your girlfriend- san's side.
Maybe girlfriend-san has a little responsibility.
That's not the case... I wonder if girlfriend-san is also responsible for you being lazy.
Well, maybe I am. I don't know if it's just the two of us. Especially at school!
Why? Well,▲彼女＊＊▲ is the best, but▲高嶺＊＊▲ is second to none!
...I don't have a boyfriend to say that to me.
Huh... do you want a boyfriend?
That's not the case! Stop it.
I knew it, girlfriend-san is wondeful.
What happened? Your studies, club activities, life attitudes... What?
Love or something like that... it's no good at all.
Somehow... Is it not fun just to have a relationhip?
Yes, that's right... in that case it's okay. It's not hard for my girlfriend!
I wonder if I can't fall in love without confidence.
Hmm, I don't know. I don't think that's true.
When I look at both you and girlfriend-san, you seem so proud of each other.
I see? Hmm... well, maybe there is such a thing!
